node.text:
I couldn’t fit all of the love in this video but this just shows how many AMAZING members of the education community we have. This video is dedicated to every single one of YOU. We love you, we appreciate you and are incredibly proud of everything you are doing.

THANK YOU!!! 🤍🤍🤍
